                     <interp inst="t18080217-44-person418" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I saw the prisoner in the servant's hall. I am sure it is the same man.</p>
               <p>Court to prisoner. Do you choose to give any account how you came in the servant's hall. - A. I never was in the servant's hall in my life.</p>
